<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٣٨ - عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ قَالَ:</span> كَانَ الْحَسَنُ وَقَتَادَةُ <span class="c2">«لَا يَرَيَانِ مِنْهُ وُضُوءًا»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>